Package tetris

Class Summary
Block Represents a Tetris block by position in the grid and color.
Coordinate Represents integer cartesian coordinates.
HighScore Handles online storage of high score data.
HighScoreTester Creates a HighScore for the purposes of writing data to the server
Tetra Represents a Tetra piece for the tetris game.
TetrisFrame Applet that displays the game
World Runs game operations and handles graphics.
